#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:14
msgid "What is Mulligan G-V2?"
msgstr "什么是留牌指南G-V2？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:16
msgid "Mulligan G-V2 is a mulligan assistant for Hearthstone, built by the team behind HSReplay.net and Hearthstone Deck Tracker."
msgstr "留牌指南G-V2是一款炉石留牌助手，与HSReplay.net和HDT插件来自同个开发团队。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:21
msgid "What does Mulligan G-V2 do?"
msgstr "留牌指南G-V2能够做什么？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:23
msgid "The Mulligan G-V2 calculates the likelihood of top players keeping or replacing a card based on specific, real-time match conditions: offered hand, player's deck, opponent's class, and player initiative. It teaches players the fundamentals of piloting a new deck by helping them to learn the core synergies between the cards in their opening hand."
msgstr "留牌指南G-V2能计算高手玩家保留或更换每张手牌的概率，并将当前对战中的各项实时信息考虑在内：起始手牌，牌库，对手职业，以及先后手。它能帮助玩家了解起手留牌中的核心配合，上手新卡组。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:32
msgid "Why does the same card have different values in the same hand?"
msgstr "为什么同样的卡牌在同样的手牌中也会显示出不同数值？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:34
msgid "When multiple copies of the same card appear in your opening hand, Mulligan G-V2 can distinguish between them. This adds an extra layer of decision-making and helps players determine whether to keep both copies or not. Mulligan G-V2 treats the leftmost copy as the first copy and the one to its right as the second. If you toggle one copy, the other will automatically become the first copy."
msgstr "在起始手牌中出现多张同样的牌时，留牌指南G-V2可以分辨出它们间的区别，提供额外决策考量，帮助玩家决定是否将它们都保留。留牌指南G-V2会将最左边的那张牌视为第一张，依次向右。如果选择换掉其中一张，另一张会自动成为第一张。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:43
msgid "Does Mulligan G-V2 support Demon Hunter Outcast?"
msgstr "留牌指南G-V2会考虑恶魔猎手的流放机制吗？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:45
msgid "Currently, Mulligan G-V2 does not take hand positions for Outcast reasons when calculating the likelihoods. We are planning on adding it in the future!"
msgstr "目前流派指南G-V2在计算概率时还不考虑流放牌在手牌中的位置，我们会后续添加这项功能！"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:51
msgid "How do I access Mulligan G-V2?"
msgstr "我该怎么获得留牌指南G-V2？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:53
msgid "Mulligan G-V2 is a Premium feature available in Hearthstone Deck Tracker. It will automatically appear when you play a Standard match."
msgstr "留牌指南G-V2是一项HDT插件的会员功能，它会在你开始对战后自动显示。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:58
msgid "Do I need to pay to use Mulligan G-V2?"
msgstr "我需要付费才能使用留牌指南G-V2吗？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:60
msgid "As a subscriber to our Premium or Bundle subscription, you can use Mulligan G-V2 as often as you want in your matches."
msgstr "作为我们的高级会员或组合套餐订阅用户，您可以在对局中随时使用留牌指南G-V2。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:64
msgid "As a free user, you can trial Mulligan G-V2 for 5 games per week. You can see how many Mulligan G-V2 trials you have remaining on the Play screen in Hearthstone."
msgstr "作为免费用户，您可以每周在5局对局中试用留牌指南G-V2。 你可以在炉石传说游戏界面上看到还有多少次留牌指南G-V2试用。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:70
msgid "Is Mulligan G-V2 available for all game modes?"
msgstr "留牌指南G-V2是否适用于所有游戏模式？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:72
msgid "Currently, it is only available in Standard, but we plan to support Wild and Arena in the future."
msgstr "目前，它只是在标准模式中才能使用，但我们计划今后支持狂野模式和竞技模式。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:77
msgid "How do I know if my decks are available for Mulligan G-V2?"
msgstr "我要怎么知道留牌指南G-V2能否适用于我的套牌？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:79
msgid "Most decks are usually supported by Mulligan G-V2. In the play screen, you can check the status of each deck. If your deck is not supported and you are a free user, it will not use one of your free trials."
msgstr "留牌指南可以适用于大部分套牌。在传统对战界面中，你可以看到每一套牌是否适用。如果你的一套牌不支持留牌指南G-V2的使用，并且如果你是免费用户，它不会消耗你的免费试用次数。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:86
msgid "Is Mulligan G-V2 available for macOS?"
msgstr "macOS端可以用留牌指南G-V2吗？"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:88
msgid "Currently, Mulligan G-V2 is not available for macOS through HSTracker. We are planning on adding support in the future!"
msgstr "HDT插件和留牌指南G-V2当前不支持macOS端。我们计划在未来添加。"

#: web/views/mulligan_gv2.py:99
msgid "Make better mulligan decisions with Mulligan Guide Version 2"
msgstr "使用留牌指南G-V2做出更好的起手留牌决策"

